Abyss

Challenging the Abyss
Access the abyss through the Events button on the world map.


*Note that it is not possible to call on friends for support in the abyss.
Codes
Codes are rules that may affect both characters and enemies in a stratum.

Each stratum or sub-stratum of the abyss will have its own set of codes, though all quests within a stratum will be bound by the same set.

Codes can restrict which characters you may bring into battle, and may enfeeble your party or enhance your enemies among other effects.
Tap on a code to see the details on its effects.

A stratum's codes will be displayed in the bottom left of the map and on each quest's preparation screen. They may also be reviewed in the pause menu during a quest.

Do note that codes take effect the moment you begin a quest, and codes affecting statuses cannot be removed in battle!
Receiving Abyss Rewards
Rewards in the abyss are given when certain quests are cleared.

Rewards may be reviewed and claimed from the Rewards window.
Gates
Tap on a gate in any of the strata to display the requirements for unlocking that gate.
